name: Global Survival: I Got the D-Rank Personnel Simulator
summary: Everyone has transmigrated to a post-apocalyptic world. At the start, each person receives a shelter and a unique talent.Lin Ye’s talent is the D-Rank Character Simulator, which allows him to enter other worlds and simulate D-Rank individuals.Lin Ye: “What the hell?!”
